      "tags": ["validation", "contract-checking", "skill-eval", "schema-validation", "test"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "顶层过程式校验脚本，无函数封装；通过 throw 在任一契约违例时中断，最终输出场景与 skill 计数。"
